data.description: Luxury living in the beautiful Meadowville Landing Community! This like new home has it ALL, except a new owner! This home sits on more than a 1/2 acre lot, parallel to the James River. This home was just built in 2022, offers 5 bedrooms, 4.5 baths, and lots of modern charm! The open concept kitchen features quartz countertops, a double wall oven and a convenient pot filler. The family room is flooded with natural light and automatic designer shades. The main level has an upgraded Butler's Pantry, a spacious home office with a coffered ceiling, and a private guest room with an ensuite. Upstairs you will find the remaining 4 Bedrooms, including the dreamy primary suite, large secondary bedrooms including 2 that share a huge Jack and Jill bath. The huge loft area is perfect for watching multiple games at once and  ample space to host and entertain. Outback you can enjoy outdoor living year round with the rear deck & stamped patio overlooking a wrought iron fenced in backyard.This home is centrally located, only minutes away from interstates 295, 95 and Fort Lee. Enjoy the luxurious amenities of the community including a pool, fitness center, playground, trails & access to the river!
